# cargo-leptos Version Compatibility

## Local Development
- cargo-leptos version: 0.2.32
- wasm-bindgen version: 0.2.100
- Command: `cargo leptos watch`

## Fly.io Deployment
- cargo-leptos version: 0.2.45 (latest, installed via Dockerfile)
- wasm-bindgen version: 0.2.104
- The Dockerfile installs the latest cargo-leptos which supports wasm-bindgen 0.2.104

## Important
Do NOT commit wasm-bindgen version changes to git. Keep it at 0.2.100 for local development.
The Fly.io build will automatically use the correct version during deployment.
